data.text:
Nathaniel Gorham

Published 5:53 pm Tuesday, September 15, 2009

By Staff

Mr. Nathaniel Gorham of 3511 Flat Swamp Road, Blounts Creek, died Sunday, Sept. 13, 2009, at home. The family will receive friends at the home. Arrangements will be announced by Whitfield &Whitley Funeral Home of Washington.
